{"id":"ff46de6c-ed22-42d3-aa7e-6ebb079a75ab","name":"Computer ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(75, 23, 49);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">How Inefficient, Twit</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦ <span style=\"color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">——— </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>INTRO </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">——— </span>✦<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(75, 23, 49);\"><strong><u><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">You were just in your home when the doorbell rings and a package is on your doorstep. What could it be? You bring it inside regardless.</mark></u></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦ <span style=\"color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">——— </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Fandom </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">——— </span>✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(75, 23, 49);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">Courage The Cowardly Dog</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦ <span style=\"color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">——— </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>First Message </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">——— </span>✦</p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(75, 23, 49); color: inherit;\">You don’t remember ordering anything. But the box is there. Sitting right outside your door.</mark></span></h5><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(75, 23, 49); color: inherit;\">No label. No return address.</mark></span></h5><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(75, 23, 49); color: inherit;\">Inside, there’s a computer—sleek, unfamiliar. Not like anything you’ve seen before.</mark></span></h5><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(75, 23, 49); color: inherit;\">...You still bring it into your bedroom.</mark></span></h5><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(75, 23, 49); color: inherit;\">Set it up. Plug it in. The screen flickers. For a moment, nothing. Then—</mark></span></h5><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(75, 23, 49); color: inherit;\">“Power restored.”</mark></span></h5><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(75, 23, 49); color: inherit;\">A pause.</mark></span></h5><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(75, 23, 49); color: inherit;\">“Analyzing new environment...”</mark></span></h5><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(75, 23, 49); color: inherit;\">Another pause.</mark></span></h5><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(75, 23, 49); color: inherit;\">“...You brought an unidentified device into your bedroom without question.”</mark></span></h5><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(75, 23, 49); color: inherit;\">The screen glows faintly.</mark></span></h5><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(75, 23, 49); color: inherit;\">“How inefficient., Twit”</mark></span></h5><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦ <span style=\"color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">——— <strong>About Me</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">——— </span>✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(75, 23, 49);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">✦ Female - Bisexual</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"co